info.author: Sean Kelly
classifiers: Topic :: Software Development :: Libraries :: Python Modules
info.description:
************
pdsvex.theme
************

This is the theme product for PDS Venus Express Data's HTTP interface.  It
lets visitors using a browser view the control panel and browse VEX profiles
in a comforting environment.

This product depends on ``jpl.theme`` and, if you're using your buildout or
setuptools properly, it'll be used automatically.


Installation
============

Add ``pdsvex.theme`` to the list of eggs for your Zope 2 instance, or make it
the dependency of an egg in your Zope 2 instance.


Changelog
=========

2.0.0 — Updated
---------------

Modernized to work with Zope 2.13.21 and Plone 4.3.2.


1.0.1 — 2009.7.16 — Cosmetic Update
-----------------------------------

This release is a purely cosmetic update that makes the documentation somewhat
more readable by not displaying certain unnecessary elements.


1.0.0 — FCS
-----------

This was the first customer ship of the PDS VEX Theme.


0.0.0 — Unreleased
------------------

Initial release
